	The two returned Sunday from Idaho for the celebration. They had been accompanying Mike's father, who is on the rodeo circuit.

	"I'm not very happy with the way they are ignoring the children. Mike knew it would happen and that's one reason he didn't want to come today," Mrs. Marshall said.


